    A representation of the model object 'Multi Net Dclf Algorithm'. Class for defining a multiple AclfNetwork Dclf algorithm object. It contains a basecase AclfNetwork object and a set of cloned AclfNetwork objects. The cloned AclfNetwork object is used to create SenAnalysisAlgorithm objects on-demand.
